Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:35.70,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}行行行...这下在宇宙里穿行可就轻松多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:50.72,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}所以...你们俩总得有个明白人吧？这鬼地方到底是哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.78,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N嘿老兄，躲柜子里试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:10.33,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你开什么玩笑？我这体型哪塞得进去——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.83,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这蓝莓精又是哪路神仙...？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N靠...这简直是Rush本尊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:50.81,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}所以...这个基金会到底是啥玩意儿？虽然像我的宇宙，但这鬼地方怎么像个...大型办公室？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N三份准备已完成一份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N三份准备已完成两份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N老兄你倒是戴上啊...不戴这玩意儿咱们可走不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.30,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*{\fs50\b1}惨叫* 怎么又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.93,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}防毒面具我根本戴不上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.13,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你瞅瞅我这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.40,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}再看这迷你版的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N行吧我不管你怎么弄，总之先把防毒面具戴上。系统规定必须佩戴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:22.63,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}系统算老几啊？！明摆着这玩意儿我戴不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N请所有在消毒室的人员注意，必须按规定穿戴全套防护装备方可继续流程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N含防面具及氧气瓶等设备,都必须佩戴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N所以我不管屋里那个大块头是啥，赶紧把面具给我戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N我真™受够了，同样的话要说多少遍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播：\N赶紧™的把面具！！立刻马上！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N得了得了——赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N听着，见到氧气瓶就拿着，待会儿用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.64,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}等等，什么叫氧气—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}*Funnint 叽里呱啦说了一通，嘿其他翻译，嗯...把彩蛋放这儿*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N快快快 GRUMBLE 给我拼了命地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.71,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*咳个不停* 我已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}广播音：\N灭菌程序启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.34,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*咳得直不起腰* 刚...刚那是啥玩意儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N后头还有好戏呢。跟...跟紧我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.27,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你该不会是在耍我吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N嘿，打听个事儿——你们那边啥情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:07.11,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这个嘛...我有群家人。有Party Grumble，戴礼帽的TopHat Grumble...呃，女王大人Queen Grumble...哦对，还有打工的Worker Grumble。我们都是一家子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N所以...你是老爹？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N*我就随便问问*
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:18.18,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}哈？想啥呢？我可是全家最小的。我们都住在DOOR 150那个巨型老巢里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N所以那是DOORS二层。你究竟怎么找到这儿的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.19,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我不知道！关键就在这里，我真的不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.68,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我从平行世界穿越过来，结果掉进了无尽虚空...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:35.02,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}后来发现个蓝色传送门，本以为能回家，结果被传送到这个鬼地方...大概是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Funnint：\N那个...下个房间其实是s——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N嘘！先别急着说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.26,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}啥？你们到底想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mekbok：\N喂，Grumble...慢慢走。我们在后面跟着。你...继续往前就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.16,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这...行吧？..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.96,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}怎-怎-怎么回事？！兄弟们？！出啥事了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.71,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不会吧...别闹了..不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.51,Grumble,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Devil Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我擦-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}*Seek的尖叫声*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}BlueAndrei：\N这个预告片会怎么开场？想表达什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Mamolousky：\N我们可以给玩家们展示一个全新角色，还有我们为游戏精心打造的新内容！那些精雕细琢的游戏细节！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N我完全赞同MAMO的看法...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:14:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N说真的...我们这段时间对游戏的新内容优化和细节打磨效果超赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N咱们真该多给玩家们看看开发进度，不然他们该觉得无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Equilibrium：\N快让他们看看我的酷炫特效！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Equilibrium：\N...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Equilibrium：\N开个玩笑啦...不过能展示确实不错...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}BlueAndrei：\N等等...那是Grumble吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N哦八成又是MIK在搞事情...老样子了...总爱往游戏里塞些奇怪模型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Equilibrium：\N不对，不是他干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTafe：\N你说不是MIK是几个意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}BlueAndrei：\N但这动作模组...太普通了...绝不是我做的。可能是Dux的手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Dux：\N我干嘛要给Grumble做动画？这游戏根本用不上它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}JohnTuff：\N那该不会是...传说中的rizzler吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这...什么情况...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}看来没人...算了，无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不过我还挺...喜欢这个房间的...等等...我怎么...变小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}搞什么？我比之前小了一大圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我的身体怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}行吧...行吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这样好像...也挺酷的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这是...什么纸条？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这该不会是...逃出这里的提示吧？看起来像那么回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这东西...说不定以后能派上用场...不过我还是继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这地方...值得探索的地方还真不少啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}海报上这些...诡异的生物是什么...难道是在供奉它们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}算了...想那么多干嘛...继续走吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}到底...还有多少道门要过啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:17:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}真是...无聊透顶...我宁愿花一整天打扫The Nest...也不想在这儿多待一秒...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不过...那个...独眼的黑色黏液怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}把..另一位Queen Grumble..化成了...一滩黑泥?...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}然后我就莫名其妙到这儿了？完全搞不懂状况...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我这是在...跟谁说话呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}别停下...Tophar...继续走...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}汉堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}老实说...这也太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}算了..能吃就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\3c&H0000FF&\4c&H0000FF&\2c&H0000FF&\c&H0000FF&}{\3c&H000000&\b1}注意：\N以下内容含闪光和刺耳噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我背后怎么有声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}怎么还...越来越响了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}消停会...别吵了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我..受不了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我说..别..吵了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}要命...你比派对Grumble还能闹!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}闭嘴!!!你这个多头怪!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你...就杵这儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}噢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我全程都在挡路...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这个房间...有点特别啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这里...是不是有什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}哇靠...这...这是什么鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&H0000FF&\2c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\4c&H0000FF&\b1}注意：\N闪光和巨大声响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}吵死了...这里的怪物能不能都给我消停点？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}啧，真够疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这...疼死我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}得...得赶紧去下一个房间！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}头好晕...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}靠...头好...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}刚...刚才那是什么动静...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我头好晕...天旋地转的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}是那张该死的纸...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我得停下来...这附近应该...有停车标志...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}好...好多了。现在缓过劲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}TopHat Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}又得...再去下一个房间了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N别-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N你怎么把它喝了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N那...可是我们最后一瓶库存了..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N行吧，行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N第一个问题——你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N其次...你到底是怎么进来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N呃...我看她好像不会说话...根本发不出声音...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N莫非她真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N要是..你能明白我说的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N就朝我指的方向看...让我知道你能听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N哦...行吧。那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N老实说...不管你是什么来头...我们压根不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N我们这儿专搞科研，配配药水啊，逮着什么做什么实验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N你...可把我们一瓶药水给糟蹋了。还搭进去不少珍贵材料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N不过说真的...我倒是不太计较这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N能不能帮我们找样东西？我们正缺这个，说不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N你把它找回来，就当是赔罪吧...毕竟刚顺走我们一瓶药水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N要是你嗯...想知道具体在哪儿找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N水晶在其他房间，不在这个房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N你可以在实验室里转转，到各个房间找找水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N不过...别走太远，那边很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N找齐水晶后，就回到这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N到时候我再教你些必须掌握的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}目的地：\N实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}目的地：\NViola的实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N你...你回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N哇哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N居...居然这么多水晶..太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.61,0:25:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N看你累坏了...先坐下休息会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.33,0:26:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N我来研究下这些水晶能派什么用场
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.28,0:26:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}30分钟后...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.28,0:26:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N我一直在考虑..既然你能理解我的意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.41,0:26:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N也许你该收下这个标识..它能帮你更好地沟通交流
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.38,0:26:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.17,0:26:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N还有这个...这是专门为你定制的科研眼镜！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.06,0:26:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Il Viola：\N太感谢你收集了这些水晶...你现在正式加入我们团队啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}刚才怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.10,0:27:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我现在算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}等等..这里是The Nest？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}怎-怎么突然这么黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.36,0:27:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.92,0:27:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}开派对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.37,0:27:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你们人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.02,0:27:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}喂喂...那个...能稍微停一会儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.50,0:27:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}喂...拜托停一下好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.94,0:27:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}跟我说说话吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.34,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}拜托了...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.15,0:27:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}搞什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.27,0:27:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你居然...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.28,0:27:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我..感觉没人愿意理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.30,0:27:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你们干嘛都不理我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.14,0:27:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.15,0:27:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这不-这太离谱了..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你的意思是...这里就剩我一个能说话的?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.58,0:27:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不是...我的意思是...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这怎么可能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.92,0:28:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}难道...这就是我小时候爸爸说的那个"宇宙奥秘"？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.49,0:28:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}该不会真是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.54,0:28:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}救命啊！！！我被困在这个宇宙里了！！谁来帮帮我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.34,0:28:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}算了...别鬼叫了...还是想办法逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.05,0:28:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}糟了...玩家要发现我了...得赶紧躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.50,0:28:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}好了...他走了...现在可以去那边看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.72,0:28:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这玩意儿...在我老家那边一直都是开着的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.82,0:28:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}要不把这些石头都挪开，钻进去看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.39,0:28:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.07,0:29:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}啥情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.59,0:29:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这地方跟我想的完全不一样...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.95,0:29:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这是个基地吗？到底是谁住在这儿啊...？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N是我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.44,0:29:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.08,0:29:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}是谁...刚才是谁在说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.93,0:29:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这声音到底从哪儿传来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N你究竟会是谁呢...？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.51,0:29:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N你为何...等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}什...什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.48,0:29:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你到底是何方神圣？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.33,0:29:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N莫非你是从平行宇宙穿越而来？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.09,0:29:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}神秘声音：\N这...没有我的协助几乎不可能实现...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.74,0:29:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}大概是吧...？可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.43,0:29:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}当时发生了惊天动地的大爆炸..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.51,0:29:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}然后我的家人们就...人间蒸发了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N唉...说来话长..我被困在这个平行宇宙里。根本无路可逃...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.11,0:29:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N我回不去原本的世界...连看着Giggles长大的机会都没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}慢着慢着...你刚才提到什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.80,0:30:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N我说我根本逃不出去！被困死在这里了！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不是不是...我是说你前面提到的，关于Giggles长大的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.29,0:30:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N我只想回到原来的世界，亲眼见证Giggles的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.98,0:30:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N你懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.08,0:30:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\NThe Growth of Giggle
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.72,0:30:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你在这个地方困了多长时间了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.72,0:30:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N实在记不清了...但肯定被困了不知多少年月
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.46,0:30:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}这样吧...能不能先报上名来？或者...从阴影里现身？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.99,0:30:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}我可不想跟空气对话...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.21,0:30:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}卧槽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.00,0:30:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Worker Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}你...你这速度...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.45,0:30:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}???：\N叫我Grumble就行...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b1}Grumble：\N{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}不过大家都叫我...
